OL,3,CTributes paid to pet shop owner whose
OL,4,Cdeath sparked murder inquiry
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to a Wiltshire
OL,7,Fbusinesswoman whose death in a head-on
OL,8,Froad collision is being treated as
OL,9,Fmurder.
OL,11,FPet shop owner Barbara Mullaney has
OL,12,Fbeen named locally as the person
OL,13,Fkilled in the crash on the B4696, near
OL,14,FRoyal Wootton Bassett.
OL,16,FDozens of flower bouquets have been
OL,17,Fleft outside the Animal Fayre pet shop
OL,18,Fin Cricklade High Street following Ms
OL,19,FMullaney's death on the evening of 30
OL,20,FJune.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
