FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1783678766
OL,3,CTributes paid to pet shop owner whose
OL,4,Cdeath sparked murder inquiry
OL,6,FOne said: "We offer our condolences,
OL,7,FAuntie Barb was such a lovely, caring
OL,8,Fvibrant lady. Always had time for a
OL,9,Fchat. She will be greatly missed. RIP
OL,10,FBarbara."
OL,12,FAnother said: "Barbara Mullaney was
OL,13,Fsadly taken from us on Tuesday 30 June.
OL,15,F"We pray for Patrick, Jeanette, Molly
OL,16,Fand all Barbara's family and friends,
OL,17,Fthat they may be comforted in the
OL,18,Fknowledge that Barbara was loved by so
OL,19,Fmany. May she be remembered always in
OL,20,Four hearts with love."
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@IO]tD@OOUwD@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
