CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1783678766
OL,3,CTributes paid to pet shop owner whose
OL,4,Cdeath sparked murder inquiry
OL,6,FOne family member posted on social
OL,7,Fmedia to thank the support of the
OL,8,FCricklade community. "Words can't
OL,9,Fdescribe the devastation," they wrote.
OL,11,F"It has been helped so much by the
OL,12,Funbelievable outpouring of literally
OL,13,Fhundreds of people whose hearts
OL,14,FBarbara has touched over the years in
OL,15,Fher little shop.
OL,17,F"The shop is bedecked with such an
OL,18,Farray of flowers. We just can't thank
OL,19,Fthem enough and tell them how proud of
OL,20,Fher this makes us feel.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@ZO]sD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1783678766
OL,3,CTributes paid to pet shop owner whose
OL,4,Cdeath sparked murder inquiry
OL,6,F"Barbara was a lady who was loved by
OL,7,Fmore people than I could ever have
OL,8,Fimagined, most of whom I have never
OL,9,Fhad the privilege of meeting."
OL,11,FAnother wrote: "A thank you from our
OL,12,Ffamily. For the beautifully
OL,13,Foverwhelming amount of love, support,
OL,14,Fhugs, offers, tributes, photos,
OL,15,Fvisits, gifts, flowers, cards, poems,
OL,16,Fmessages and of course ` parsley for
OL,17,FWorzel.
OL,19,F"It goes without saying that, as is
OL,20,Fthe rest of Cricklade community, we
OL,21,Fare beyond devastated."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@^O]sD@POU{D@AOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
