OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1783678766
OL,3,CTributes paid to pet shop owner whose
OL,4,Cdeath sparked murder inquiry
OL,6,FWiltshire Police said the collision
OL,7,Finvolved an orange Peugeot 107
OL,8,Ftravelling southbound and a black
OL,9,FVauxhall Astra travelling northbound.
OL,11,FThe driver of the Peugeot, a woman in
OL,12,Fher 70s, was declared dead at the
OL,13,Fscene.
OL,15,FA passenger in the Vauxhall, a teenage
OL,16,Fgirl, suffered serious injuries in the
OL,17,Fcollision and was taken to hospital
OL,18,Fbefore being discharged.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
