OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1783678766
OL,3,CTributes paid to pet shop owner whose
OL,4,Cdeath sparked murder inquiry
OL,6,FPolice said the driver of the
OL,7,FVauxhall, a man aged 43, has been
OL,8,Ffurther arrested on suspicion of
OL,9,Fmurder and attempted murder.
OL,11,FHe was taken to hospital for treatment
OL,12,Ffollowing the collision and has now
OL,13,Fbeen taken into custody for
OL,14,Fquestioning.
OL,16,FThe Wiltshire force has made a
OL,17,Fmandatory referral to the Independent
OL,18,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC) due
OL,19,Fto previous involvement with the
OL,20,Fsuspect.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
