PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1783678766
OL,3,CTributes paid to pet shop owner whose
OL,4,Cdeath sparked murder inquiry
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Phil Walker,
OL,7,Fwho is leading the investigation,
OL,8,Fsaid: "My thoughts continue to be with
OL,9,Fthe victim's family and all that knew
OL,10,Fher.
OL,12,F"Her next of kin have been informed of
OL,13,Fthis latest development in the
OL,14,Finvestigation and they continue to be
OL,15,Fsupported by specially trained
OL,16,Fofficers."
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@AOUxD@JO]
